Detailed Description

cvmx_gser::_lane::_rx_ctle_ctrl

These are the RAW PCS per-lane RX CTLE control registers. These registers are reset by hardware only during chip cold reset. The values of the CSR fields in these registers do not change during chip warm or soft resets.
